title: Apple Reports Q1 Earnings Beat
description: Apple Inc. reported quarterly earnings of $1.25 per share, beating analyst estimates of $1.15. Revenue grew 15% year-over-year to $95 billion.

title: Tesla Misses EPS Expectations Despite Revenue Growth
description: Tesla Inc. reported Q4 earnings of $0.85 per share, missing expectations of $1.10, though revenue increased 20% to $25 billion.

title: Microsoft Delivers Strong Fiscal Year Results
description: Microsoft Corporation posted full-year profit of $72 billion, exceeding analyst forecasts on cloud computing strength.
